{"tid":992700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方]女睡到一半衣褲全濕　驚醒一看被男人露鳥射尿","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T11:33:40.000Z","uid":179810,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33bbf7fdc195545d489d558f55bab99fe7d9674c","tid":992700,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190118/1502818/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190118%2F1502818%2F&d=aJoDg7%2FdIljMrna1Ylq5yEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0d4149e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190118%2F1502818%2F&h=dbca296b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190118/1502818/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190118/640_349b21a9288f31a926ecd0ad407fe673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190118%2F640_349b21a9288f31a926ecd0ad407fe673.jpg&h=bd4020f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國一名女子，周日（13日）凌晨在火車上睡覺時，突然感到褲子和衣服全部濕透，睜開眼睛一看，才驚覺是一名男乘客正對著她當眾放尿。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n警方表示，這起「隨地小便」發生在由廣州開往大連的T367次特快列車上。女子當時正在睡覺，卻突然覺得有一陣「溫暖」，且衣褲全濕，驚醒後發現38歲、來自遼寧朝陽的闞姓男乘客正當眾脫褲向她射尿。乘警（火車上的駐警）到場時，闞男已尿完，光著下半身坐在女子對面。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n闞男後來向警方供稱，前一晚上車前，曾與朋友一起喝了一斤多的酒，本想在車上好好睡一覺，但大概是因為喝到太醉、太亢奮，才會藉著酒勁，向人露鳥、放尿。闞男已被罰行政拘留10天。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n蝗狗射尿"},{"pid":"eb0ce2a49b54271a427eddde177718b5d8881f79","tid":992700,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"肉便器"},{"pid":"df2507c242ee8a5bac654cf7614fdcf752e82c4f","tid":992700,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822dd311684a6d729a6d140cc9a392c999e022f7","tid":992700,"uid":25367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:33:40.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞真係寧舍弱智，咩射尿、放尿都寫得出"}]}